	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am currently level 28. At level 18 i started doing the burning rapier quest. I camped the blackburrow cask and the blackburrow gnoll skins for like 2 weeks. I got my high lvl friend to get the blood spirits. Then i went and lvld up a few levels and relized i had better weapons than the burning rapier. For the effort involed to get the rapier it is not a very good quest item at all- their are high lvl creatures rare spawns rare drops and at the end you have to pay 560PP!!!! A couple more hundred PP and you can get yourself a crystaline spider fang or a kaelorek dar spine razor on xev. Verant should defanitely upgrade the damage/delay ratio to something acceptable like 9 20 or 10 20 for all the effort and PP you put into it. Just my 2 cp<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
